Timers Module functions:

- setTimeout(cb, delay) — execute callback ONCE after delay (ms).

- setInterval(cb, delay) — execute callback REPEATEDLY every delay (ms).

- setImmediate(cb) — execute callback in the CHECK PHASE — after I/O events.

- process.nextTick(cb) — execute callback AFTER current operation and BEFORE the promise, next event loop — highest priority.

